Package com.rpfsoftwares.systembuilderlib.annotation

Contains all annotation types necessary to help you when using this library.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Date
    Annotation type used to program elements that must be placed on a JDateChooser with the given format and then added to a JForm
    Disabled
    Annotation type used to program elements that should be added to a JForm, but set as Disabled (Enabled = false)
    ForeignKey
    Annotation type used to program elements that are a foreign key in another table
    Formatted
    Annotation type used to program elements that must be placed on a JFormattedTextField with the given format and added to a JForm
    Interval
    Annotation type used to program elements that must have an interval on a int JSpinner added to a JForm
    IntervalReal
    Annotation type used to program elements that must have an interval on a double JSpinner added to a JForm
    LongText
    Annotation type used to program elements that should be added to a JForm as an JTextArea
    MultiValues
    Annotation type used to program elements that must be placed on a JComboBox added to a JForm
    Secure
    Annotation type used to program elements that should be added to a JForm as a JPasswordField
    Skip
    Annotation type used to program elements that should not be added to a JForm

Package com.rpfsoftwares.systembuilderlib.annotation Description

Contains all annotation types necessary to help you when using this library.
